rows.label: qst201515_msg0020
rows.name: And that about wraps that up.

rows.label: qst201515_msg0001
rows.name:
Does it, though? The bad guys got
away. What if they end up trying to
do the same thing again?

rows.label: qst201515_msg0002
rows.name:
I dunno about that. The bad guys got
away. What's to say they won't try
and pull the same thing again?

rows.label: qst201515_msg0003
rows.name:
For the time being, perhaps. But with
the perpetrators still at large, there's
no telling what they might do now...

rows.label: qst201515_msg0004
rows.name:
Yeah, for now maybe. But the bad
guys got away. What if they end up
trying to pull another stunt like this?

rows.label: qst201515_msg0005
rows.name:
Oh, I don't think you'll have to worry
about that.

rows.label: qst201515_msg0006
rows.name:
That machine was a rare salvager find.
I doubt they'll ever be able to recreate
anything like it.

rows.label: qst201515_msg0007
rows.name:
And once they arrest the scientist
who was processing the Thanatitan,
they won't be able to make any more.

rows.label: qst201515_msg0008
rows.name:
Which means that this will be the first
and last time they ever try to inject
the stuff into the Divine Beast.

rows.label: qst201515_msg0009
rows.name: Let's hope so...

rows.label: qst201515_msg0010
rows.name:
Anyway, I have to hand it to you,
Azami. You did a bang-up job.

rows.label: qst201515_msg0011
rows.name: Right... I guess we're good, then.

rows.label: qst201515_msg0012
rows.name:
Anyway, nice work there, Azami.
I'm impressed.

rows.label: qst201515_msg0013
rows.name: I do hope that's true...

rows.label: qst201515_msg0014
rows.name:
In any case, it seems our mission
is accomplished. You've done well,
Azami.

rows.label: qst201515_msg0015
rows.name: Fingers crossed it's all over then...

rows.label: qst201515_msg0016
rows.name:
Anyhow, looks like our work here's
done. Bloody good work, Azami!

rows.label: qst201515_msg0017
rows.name:
What, that's all the thanks I get?
Come on now, I deserve a little
more credit than that...

rows.label: qst201515_msg0018
rows.name: Uh, I thought I was thanking you...?

rows.label: qst201515_msg0019
rows.name:
Huh? I thought I was being pretty
grateful to you...

rows.label: qst201515_msg0021
rows.name:
Not satisfied? I had intended to
praise your efforts...

rows.label: qst201515_msg0022
rows.name:
What, you want more praise than that?
What more do you want?

rows.label: qst201515_msg0023
rows.name:
After everything I've done, the least you
could do is ask me out on a date...

rows.label: qst201515_msg0024
rows.name:
Well, at least I got to spend time with
my darling Driver, so I can't complain,
I suppose. I'll forgive you.

rows.label: qst201515_msg0025
rows.name:
I had hoped the mission would last
a little longer so I could spend more
time with you...

rows.label: qst201515_msg0026
rows.name:
I really wanted to keep you all to
myself... Oh well.

rows.label: qst201515_msg0031
rows.name:
As for that man who tricked us...
Does he really think he can lie to
me and get away with it...?

rows.label: qst201515_msg0032
rows.name:
If he thinks he can escape me, he's
sorely mistaken. I'll find him, and I'll
make him pay.

rows.label: qst201515_msg0033
rows.name:
Let's see...
A thousand lashes should suffice.

rows.label: qst201515_msg0034
rows.name: Heh heh heh...
